author: Hannah Paine
title: Ruby Rose packs Jessica Origliasso's suitcase
text:
They've been virtually inseparable since rekindling their love last year.
And Jessica Origliasso, 32, has lifted the lid on her rare time apart from girlfriend Ruby Rose , 30, revealing the Orange Is The New Black actress still packs her suitcase and styles outfits for the singer.
The Veronicas twin made the confession via Instagram , alongside a photo of her wearing a jumper plastered with Ruby Rose's face.
'When your girlfriend packs your entire suitcase': Jessica Origliasso reveals luggage arrangements with beau Ruby Rose while wearing a jumper plastered with the actress' face
Jessica posted the photo on Friday, revealing she was currently visiting Dubai.
The petite beauty looked stunning with cat eye makeup and a strong red lipstick, wearing her hair in a messy half up-do with shorter strands framing her face.
She donned an over-sized white jumper which featured an image of a bandanna-wearing Ruby Rose.
Travel plans: Jessica reveals that even when apart, Ruby packs her suitcase and acts as a makeup and clothing 'stylist' for the singer
The photo appeared to have been taken inside a hotel room, with open luggage visible in the background behind Jessica.
'When your girlfriend packs your entire suitcase, and is long distance make up artist and stylist for your outfits in Dubai and the only thing you pack for yourself is a sweater of her face @rubyrose,' she said.
Jessica and Ruby first dated in 2008 and rekindled their romance after starring in the video clip for The Veronicas' single On Your Side.
'She is the most amazing person': Ruby gushing about the singer to Entertainment Tonight on Thursday
The couple has since made no secret of their affection for one another, with Ruby gushing about the singer to Entertainment Tonight on Thursday.
'She's always such a moral support for me and a moral compass,' Ruby said at the Los Angeles premiere of xXx: Return of Xander Cage.
'She is the most amazing person,' she continued.
'We just jam every night': The Orange Is The New Black star has also offered a glimpse of her domestic life with The Veronicas singer
The Orange Is The New Black star also offered a glimpse of her domestic life with The Veronicas singer.
'We just jam every night. We just play music and sing and cook dinner, and she's amazing,' she said.
Jessica supported her lady love by attending the premiere with her twin sister Lisa Origliasso.
